        <div class="bb-intro-module__card-description">
                    <p>The Supreme Court created its <a href="https://www.propublica.org/article/supreme-court-adopts-ethics-code-scotus-thomas-alito-crow">first-ever code of conduct</a> after we reported that justices repeatedly failed to disclose gifts and travel from the ultrawealthy.</p>

