        style="object-position: 49.54% 25.61%;"            />

        <div class="bb-intro-module__card-description">
                    <p>The Idaho Legislature <a href="https://www.propublica.org/article/idaho-legislature-approves-funding-for-school-repairs">approved $2 billion for school repairs</a> after we revealed just how poor the conditions were in the state’s crumbling schools.</p>

            </div>
</div>

        
<div class="bb-intro-module__card ">
            
    


    <img
        class="bb-intro-module__art"
        alt=""
