    <div class="story-card__description">
                
        <h3 class="story-card__hed" >
            <a href="https://www.propublica.org/article/formaldehyde-epa-report-public-health">
                                    EPA Report Finds That Formaldehyde Presents an “Unreasonable Risk” to Public Health
                            </a>
        </h3>

        <p class="story-card__dek" >
                            The report was published weeks after a ProPublica investigation found that the chemical causes more cancer than any other toxic air pollutant and can trigger asthma, miscarriages and fertility problems.
                    </p>

        <p class="story-card__byline">
            by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/sharon-lerner">Sharon Lerner</a>,             <time class="timestamp" datetime="2025-01-03EST17:00">Jan. 3, 5 p.m. EST</time>
        </p>

            </div>
</div>
                    


        
                    
<div class="story-card story-card--standard">
    
    

                    
                    
    
