    <div class="story-card__description">
                
        <h3 class="story-card__hed" >
            <a href="https://www.propublica.org/article/how-to-reduce-formaldehyde-home-exposure">
                                    How to Reduce Formaldehyde Exposure in Your Home
                            </a>
        </h3>

        <p class="story-card__dek" >
                            The underregulated toxic chemical can be found in common household items from couches to clothes. We asked experts how you can reduce your exposure.
                    </p>

        <p class="story-card__byline">
            by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/topher-sanders">Topher Sanders</a>,             <time class="timestamp" datetime="2024-12-09EST05:05">Dec. 9, 2024, 5:05 a.m. EST</time>
        </p>

