    <div class="story-card__description">
                
        <h3 class="story-card__hed" >
            <a href="https://www.propublica.org/article/ap3-oath-keepers-militia-mole">
                                    The Militia and the Mole
                            </a>
        </h3>

        <p class="story-card__dek" >
                            Outraged by the Jan. 6 Capitol riot, a wilderness survival trainer spent years undercover climbing the ranks of right-wing militias. 

He didn’t tell police or the FBI. He didn’t tell family or friends. The one person he told was a ProPublica reporter.
                    </p>

        <p class="story-card__byline">
            by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/joshua-kaplan">Joshua Kaplan</a>,             <time class="timestamp" datetime="2025-01-04EST05:00">Jan. 4, 5 a.m. EST</time>
        </p>

